What has really been exposed in the U.S. and in Europe is the devastating effect of cuts to public health care resources combined with privatization.
For a massive expenditure of public resources to be directed to develop a vaccine.
Provide immediate safe public space to house the homeless where they can have access to free medical resources.
The only reason they’re now giving workers some assistance is to try to prop up the capitalist economy.
We can’t let the rich demonize the sick and vulnerable and let the billionaires who created this crisis off the hook.